Photographer of the First Lady, Hajiya Aisha Buhari, Mr Mohammed Yusuf Ovajimo, is dead. Director of Information in the Office of the First Lady, Suleiman Haruna, announced this on his Facebook page. Though there were no details on his death, the deceased was described in glowing languages. The statement reads: “Today we lost Mohammed Yusuf Ovajimo a professional photographer of the First Lady of Nigeria. “He is an accomplished professional with loads of skill and great human relations. He will be greatly missed. May his soul rest in perfect peace.